title: Joe Haden Released, Stafford Gets PAID! (Football 08/30)
description:
Will Brinson and Pete Prisco break down the latest news surrounding Joe Haden's release (4:40), take a look at Matthew Stafford's contract and explain why it was a smart move from the Lions (8:50), talk about Ezekiel Elliott's status for his suspension (15:30) and then dive into some fantasy football chatter, debating whether Doug Baldwin is worth a second round pick, when you can take Elliott and if Jay Ajayi and/or Michael Thomas can end up being the top performer at their respective position (25:40).
